<author>jwrj stybnz</author>
<title>ạ̉njz yạ rby qṣdk by</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạản̊jiz̊ yā rabĩy qaṣ̊daka bī
 kẖazafuⁿ ại̹nĩy baẙna yadaẙk̊
 kayĩf̊ ḥayātī kamā tasẖāʾ̊
 ạảẘdaʿ̊tu kulã qal̊bī ladaẙk̊

[V2]
 2- ạản̊jiz̊ yā rabĩy qaṣ̊daka bī
 fāi̹nã qal̊bī wāhiⁿ jarīḥ̊
 kulũ ậmālī fīka rabĩy
 fāản̊ta niʿ̊ma ạl̊kẖilũ ạlṣãḥīḥ̊

[V3]
 3- ạản̊jiz̊ yā rabĩy qaṣ̊daka bī
 ạản̊ta liqal̊bī kẖaẙru murīḥ̊
 ạim̊lạ̊̉ ḥayātī birūḥika
 kaẙ yatajalãy̱ fīã ạl̊masīḥ̊</lyrics>
</song>